fields.name: version
fields.description: Message version (0x00 for this version)

fields.name: reserved0
fields.description: Reserved

fields.name: iTOW
fields.description: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch. See the description of iTOW for details.

fields.name: dur
fields.description: Passed survey-in observation time

fields.name: meanX
fields.description: Current survey-in mean position ECEF X coordinate

fields.name: meanY
fields.description: Current survey-in mean position ECEF Y coordinate

fields.name: meanZ
fields.description: Current survey-in mean position ECEF Z coordinate

fields.name: meanXHP
fields.description: Current high-precision survey-in mean position ECEF X coordinate. Must be in the range -99..+99. The current survey-in mean position ECEF X coordinate, in units of cm, is given by meanX + (0.01 * meanXHP)

fields.name: meanYHP
fields.description: Current high-precision survey-in mean position ECEF Y coordinate. Must be in the range -99..+99. The current survey-in mean position ECEF Y coordinate, in units of cm, is given by meanY + (0.01 * meanYHP)

fields.name: meanZHP
fields.description: Current high-precision survey-in mean position ECEF Z coordinate. Must be in the range -99..+99. The current survey-in mean position ECEF Z coordinate, in units of cm, is given by meanZ + (0.01 * meanZHP)

fields.name: reserved1
fields.description: Reserved

fields.name: meanAcc
fields.description: Current survey-in mean position accuracy

fields.name: obs
fields.description: Number of position observations used during survey-in

fields.name: valid
fields.description: Survey-in position validity flag, 1 = valid, otherwise 0

fields.name: active
fields.description: Survey-in in-progress flag, 1 = in-progress, otherwise 0
